[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "The name of the hebrews began already to be every where renowned, and rumors about them ran abroad.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000001_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000001_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Accordingly they sent ambassadors to one another, and exhorted one another to defend themselves, and to endeavor to destroy these men.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Those that induced the rest to do so, were such as inhabited Gobolitis and Petra.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "These proceedings of the people of those countries occasioned perplexity and trouble to Moses, who expected no such warlike preparations.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "So he exhorted them to be courageous at this time, and to look upon their entire prosperity to depend on the present conquest of their enemies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "The young men he charged to obey their elders, and the elders to hearken to their leader.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "He also appointed a small party of the armed men to be near the water, and to take care of the children, and the women, and of the entire camp.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000003_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000003_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Moses also kept awake, teaching joshua after what manner he should order his camp.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000003_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000003_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "He also gave a particular exhortation to the principal men of the hebrews, and encouraged the whole army as it stood armed before him. And when he had thus animated the army, both by his words and works, and prepared every thing, he retired to a mountain, and committed the army to God and to joshua.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "When this was done, the hebrews conquered the Amalekites by main force; and indeed they had all perished, unless the approach of the night had obliged the hebrews to desist from killing any more.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000004_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000004_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "So the hebrews now valued themselves upon their courage, and claimed great merit for their valor; and they perpetually inured themselves to take pains, by which they deemed every difficulty might be surmounted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000004_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000004_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Such were the consequences of this battle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "On the next day, Moses stripped the dead bodies of their enemies, and gathered together the armor of those that were fled, and gave rewards to such as had signalized themselves in the action; and highly commended joshua, their general, who was attested to by all the army, on account of the great actions he had done.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Nor was any one of the hebrews slain; but the slain of the enemy's army were too many to be enumerated.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "So Moses offered sacrifices of thanksgiving to God, and built an altar, which he named The Lord the Conqueror.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "He also foretold that the Amalekites should utterly be destroyed; and that hereafter none of them should remain, because they fought against the hebrews, and this when they were in the wilderness, and in their distress also.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Moreover, he refreshed the army with feasting.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "And thus did they fight this first battle with those that ventured to oppose them, after they were gone out of Egypt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "CHAPTER three.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "That Moses Kindly Received His Father In Law, Jethro, When He Came To Him To Mount Sinai.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Now when Raguel, Moses's father in law, understood in what a prosperous condition his affairs were, he willingly came to meet him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "And Moses and his children, and pleased himself with his coming.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "And when he had offered sacrifice, he made a feast for the multitude, near the Bush he had formerly seen; which multitude, every one according to their families, partook of the feast.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "But Aaron and his family took Raguel, and sung hymns to God, as to Him who had been the author procurer of their deliverance and their freedom.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "They also praised their conductor, as him by whose virtue it was that all things had succeeded with them. Raguel also, in his eucharistical oration to Moses, made great encomiums upon the whole multitude; and he could not but admire Moses for his fortitude, and that humanity he had shewn in the delivery of his friends.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "CHAPTER four.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "How Raguel Suggested To Moses To Set His People In Order, Under Their Rulers Of Thousands, And Rulers Of Hundreds, Who Lived Without Order Before; And How Moses Complied In All Things With His Father In Law's Admonition.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Raguel however said nothing to him at that time, as not desirous to be any hinderance to such as had a mind to make use of the virtue of their conductor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000009_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000009_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "Permit, therefore, the determination of common causes to be done by others, but do thou reserve thyself to the attendance on God only, and look out for methods of preserving the multitude from their present distress.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000009_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000009_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "But if any great cause arise, let them bring the cognizance of it before the rulers of a higher dignity; but if any great difficulty arise that is too hard for even their determination, let them send it to thee.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4699_12472_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4699/12472/4699_12472_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4699",
        "content": "This was the admonition of Raguel; and Moses received his advice very kindly, and acted according to his suggestion.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    }
]